好了 我有决定权 而我说我们要专注练习计划好的歌单
Okay, I have the pitch pipe, and I say that we focus on the set list as planned.

977
01:06:10,133 --> 01:06:12,676
从现在起 没有时间再浪费在爱好
From now on, there will be no more wasting time with work

978
01:06:12,761 --> 01:06:16,305
学校 男朋友 或者同伴上了
or school or boyfriends or partners.

979
01:06:16,389 --> 01:06:18,474
抱歉 辛西娅・罗丝
Sorry, Cynthia Rose.

980
01:06:19,559 --> 01:06:21,852
