But Aubrey, this stuff is pretty cool. I mean...

981
01:06:21,936 --> 01:06:24,104
好了 明天彩排 八点整
Okay. Rehearsal tomorrow, 8:00 a.m. sharp.

982
01:06:36,409 --> 01:06:37,701
嘿!
Hey!

983
01:06:39,371 --> 01:06:42,414
这是我的作品! 你现在在放我的歌曲!
This is my track! You're playing my song right now!

984
01:06:42,916 --> 01:06:45,209
真是太了不起了! 你喜欢吗?
That is awesome! You like it?

985
01:06:45,335 --> 01:06:48,128
你放在广播上了! 太惊奇了!
You put it on the radio! That is amazing!

986
01:06:48,546 --> 01:06:50,172
让人受不了的节奏
It's a sick beat.

987
01:06:51,424 --> 01:06:53,300
没错 我一直觉得她的节奏挺让人受不了的
Yeah, I always thought her beats were pretty sick.

988
01:06:53,385 --> 01:06:56,387
嘿 贝卡 听着 春假的时候 我想你来值夜班
Hey, Becky, listen, spring break, I want you to take the night shift.

989
01:06:56,471 --> 01:06:57,513
放你的音乐
Play your music.

990
01:06:58,390 --> 01:07:02,601
这首歌 车库摇滚DJ的版本非常出色 但是你的呢? 更好
The DJ at the Garage does a brilliant version of this, but yours? It's better.

991
01:07:02,936 --> 01:07:04,186
是的 没错
Yeah, it is.

992
01:07:04,270 --> 01:07:07,439
我今晚要听她的 我觉得你应该... 你也应该来
I'm gonna listen to her tonight. I think you should... you should come with.

993
01:07:07,524 --> 01:07:09,066
我有事情
I have a thing.

994
01:07:09,776 --> 01:07:11,193
空姐训练?
Flight attendant training?

995
01:07:11,277 --> 01:07:15,114
是巴顿贝拉合唱团 我今晚有半决赛
It's Barden Bellas. I have the semi-finals tonight.

996
01:07:15,615 --> 01:07:19,201
真的? 我无法想象你会无伴奏合唱
Really? I did not have you pegged as an a cappella girl.

997
01:07:19,285 --> 01:07:21,203
那是因为你没有我了解贝卡
That's 'cause you don't know Becky like I do.

998
01:07:21,287 --> 01:07:22,705
晚上见
See you tonight.

999
01:07:40,098 --> 01:07:42,474
没事 你们群妞儿别担心 我来处理
Okay, don't you flat-butts worry, I got this.

1000
01:07:42,642 --> 01:07:44,309
我只要加下油就行了
I'm just gonna pump and dump.

1001
01:07:45,478 --> 01:07:46,520
我不管你说什么
I don't care what you say.

1002
01:07:46,604 --> 01:07:49,523
西斯科的现场 我所看过的最好的表演
Sisqo live, best performance ever, I've ever seen.

1003
01:07:49,607 --> 01:07:51,400
"皮带歌"不是他唯一的成功作
"Thong Song" isn't his only hit. Yeah.

1004
01:07:55,113 --> 01:07:56,155
不是吗? 这是认真的
All right? That's serious.

1005
01:07:56,239 --> 01:07:57,364
哟 邦博尔 那不是胖艾米吗?
Yo, Bump, is that Fat Amy?

1006
01:07:58,324 --> 01:08:00,075
唐纳德 减速! 慢点!
Donald, slow down! Slow down!

1007
01:08:00,160 --> 01:08:01,910
耶! 很好!
Yeah! All right!

1008
01:08:02,662 --> 01:08:05,038
嘿 艾米? 搞破坏咯!
Hey, Amy? Sabotage!

1009
01:08:10,879 --> 01:08:12,546
