Oh, shit. Bumper threw a big-ass burrito at me.

1018
01:08:37,030 --> 01:08:40,741
我要杀了他 我发誓 我要把他打成奶油蛋糕
I'm gonna kill him, I swear. I'm gonna finish him like a cheesecake.

1019
01:09:05,975 --> 01:09:07,726
你这里还有一点东西
You've got yourself a little something there.

1020
01:09:07,811 --> 01:09:10,395
别管了 它能一直点燃我的恨意
Just leave it. It fuels my hate fire.

1021
01:09:50,061 --> 01:09:51,520
哦 天呐
Oh, my God.

1022
01:10:22,427 --> 01:10:23,969
那是... 是...
It's a... It's...

1023
01:10:26,347 --> 01:10:27,347
哦
Oh.

1024
01:10:27,473 --> 01:10:29,141
搞什么?
What the hell?

1025
01:10:29,559 --> 01:10:33,645
呃... 那真是很酷 实际上 我想我们没油了
Um... It's pretty cool, actually. I think we're just running out of gas.

1026
01:10:34,022 --> 01:10:35,939
不 不可能 你刚刚才加满的
No, that can't be. You just filled the tank.

1027
01:10:36,024 --> 01:10:37,816
是的 我加了
Yeah, I did.

1028
01:10:39,319 --> 01:10:43,822
