Five minutes, Bellas.

1047
01:12:16,958 --> 01:12:18,834
- 他哪儿来的?  - 嘘!
- Where did he come from?  - Shh!

1048
01:12:18,918 --> 01:12:22,587
完了 我们不可能打败脚注合唱团和刺儿头小子的
It's over. There's no way we can beat the Footnotes and the Trebles.

1049
01:12:52,452 --> 01:12:54,202
哇! 这个小个子真能唱
Whoo! That little peanut can sing.

1050
01:12:54,287 --> 01:12:57,581
真的不错 不过 盖尔 在我听来 他好像还没发育完全
He really can. It sounds to me, though, Gail, like his boys haven't dropped yet,

1051
01:12:57,665 --> 01:12:58,874
你懂我意思的
if you know what I mean.

1052
01:12:58,958 --> 01:13:02,502
如果你指他的下体 我懂 约翰 真的懂
If you mean his testicles, then I do, John. I do. I really do.

1053
01:13:02,587 --> 01:13:03,962
过来 过来
A-ca-huddle, now.

1054
01:13:04,672 --> 01:13:07,716
只有前两名能进入决赛 我们必须要打败他们其中一个
The top two teams go to the finals, so we just have to beat one of them.

1055
01:13:07,800 --> 01:13:12,471
只要我们完完全全按照排练的表演 就能成功 好吗? 完完全全
And if we do it exactly how we rehearsed it, we will get there, okay? Exactly.

1056
01:13:15,475 --> 01:13:16,558
伸出手
Hands in.

1057
01:13:18,144 --> 01:13:19,352
数到三时 还是数完三之后?
On three or after three?

1058
01:13:19,937 --> 01:13:21,146
算了 上吧
Screw it. Let's just do it.

1059
01:13:21,230 --> 01:13:23,815
掌声有请出巴顿贝拉合唱团!
Put your hands together for the Barden Bellas!

1060
01:13:25,193 --> 01:13:27,027
好的 贝拉要出场了
Okay, the Bellas are coming out.

1061
