What the hell, Beca? Were you trying to screw us up?

1072
01:14:53,489 --> 01:14:54,531
你当真吗?
Are you serious?

1073
01:14:54,615 --> 01:14:56,783
简单申明 这并不是贝卡的独唱秀
Newsflash. This isn't the Beca show.

1074
01:14:56,868 --> 01:14:59,327
好吧 很抱歉搅乱了你的演出
Okay, I'm sorry that I messed you up,

1075
01:14:59,412 --> 01:15:02,289
但你可能没注意到吧 我们演唱的时候 大家都快睡着了
but in case you hadn't noticed, everybody pretty much dozed off during our set.

1076
01:15:02,415 --> 01:15:05,000
