Aubrey, it actually went really well.

1094
01:16:01,432 --> 01:16:02,724
够了 克洛伊!
Chloe, stop!

1095
01:16:02,808 --> 01:16:04,559
抱歉 噢 天啊 好吧
Excuse me. Oh, my God. Okay.

1096
01:16:05,770 --> 01:16:08,563
