1099
01:16:25,039 --> 01:16:28,625
很不幸 巴顿的另一支合唱团 贝拉合唱团 不幸出局
Unfortunately, Barden's other group, the Bellas, do not advance,

1100
01:16:28,709 --> 01:16:33,505
毕业班的奥布里・柏森失去了一洗去年呕吐门的机会
and senior Aubrey Posen loses her chance to redeem herself from last year's Pukegate.

1101
01:16:41,973 --> 01:16:43,723
