这样感觉真好
And that's pretty cool.

1284
01:30:24,169 --> 01:30:26,754
这就是我啦 下一个吧
So, that's me. Someone else please go.

1285
01:30:29,007 --> 01:30:30,007
好吧
Okay.

1286
01:30:32,677 --> 01:30:38,432
春假时 我做了一个勇敢的决定 切除我的声带小结
Over spring break, I made the courageous decision to remove my nodes.

1287
01:30:40,018 --> 01:30:44,939
我知道 医生说 我也许永远不能再唱
I know. The doctor said that I can't sing above a G-sharp,

1288
01:30:45,899 --> 01:30:47,274
升G调以上的音了
maybe ever.

1289
01:30:47,943 --> 01:30:51,028
我当时以为这个赛季结束了
I thought the season was over.

1290
01:30:54,991 --> 01:30:57,201
没事 没事的
It's okay. It's okay.

1291
01:30:59,496 --> 01:31:02,540
贝卡 我们该怎么办?
Beca, what do we do?

1292
01:31:12,175 --> 01:31:13,592
抱歉
I'm sorry.

1293
01:31:14,386 --> 01:31:15,511
那就别在这儿唱了
Maybe not here.

1294
01:31:16,638 --> 01:31:19,431
好了 我们开始混音吧
All right. Let's remix this business.

1295
01:31:20,433 --> 01:31:25,020
奥布里 能为我们选首歌吗?
Aubrey, would you pick a song for us, please?

1296
01:31:25,105 --> 01:31:27,606
布鲁诺・马尔斯的"皆应是你"
Bruno Mars, Just The Way You Are.

1297
01:31:29,401 --> 01:31:32,444
好的 克洛伊 你可以起个头吗?
Okay. Chloe, are you okay to take the lead?

1298
01:31:32,529 --> 01:31:33,571
好
Yeah.

1299
01:33:18,343 --> 01:33:19,343
伸出手
Hands in.

1300
01:33:23,390 --> 01:33:25,432
一 二...
One, two...

1301
01:33:27,227 --> 01:33:28,435
什么声音?
What was that?

1302
01:33:28,520 --> 01:33:30,187
不知道 我从未发出过这个音
I don't know, I've never made that sound before.

1303
01:33:30,272 --> 01:33:33,107
不过你现在医治过的声带 可以唱低音了
Yo, but with your messed up vocal cords, you could hit the bass notes.

1304
01:33:33,525 --> 01:33:35,192
你知道这代表什么吗?
Do you know what that means?

1305
01:33:35,277 --> 01:33:36,485
莉莉 怎么了?
Yes, Lilly?

1306
01:33:36,569 --> 01:33:38,696
我想这样我有技巧可以帮到大家
I think I have something that can help us out.

1307
01:33:39,906 --> 01:33:42,032
亲爱的 不需要你大声喊的
Excuse me, bitch, you don't need to shout.

1308
01:33:42,200 --> 01:33:44,159
可别说大话啊
Okay, don't get mouthy.

1309
01:33:59,676 --> 01:34:00,968
欢迎来到2012
Welcome to the finals

1310
01:34:01,052 --> 01:34:04,930
大学生无伴奏合唱国际锦标赛
of the 2012 International Championship of Collegiate A Cappella.

1311
01:34:05,515 --> 01:34:09,101
林肯中心今晚蓬荜生辉 正是因为有了这群
Lincoln Center is proud to welcome back all of these young hopefuls tonight

1312
01:34:09,185 --> 01:34:12,813
用嘴巴创造音乐的年轻人 他们都希望获得今晚的冠军
who are hoping to win a trophy by making music with their mouths.

1313
01:34:20,613 --> 01:34:23,198
盖尔 我跟你说 今晚将是美好的一晚
This is gonna be a big night, and I tell you, Gail,

1314
01:34:23,325 --> 01:34:26,160
- 闭上眼睛  - 我已经闭了
- if you can just shut your eyes. - I'm doing it.

1315
01:34:26,244 --> 01:34:29,371
闭上眼睛 忘掉什么规则
Shut your eyes and get rid of all the a-ca-politics,

1316
01:34:29,581 --> 01:34:33,834
只要记住 在纽约城的林肯中心
then you can remember that being at Lincoln Center, in the Big Apple,

1317
01:34:33,918 --> 01:34:38,589
在这个历史悠久的舞台上演唱 是每个无伴奏演唱者的梦想
and singing on this storied stage is the dream of every a cappella singer.

1318
01:34:38,673 --> 01:34:40,382
你说对了 约翰
You said it, John.

1319
01:34:56,107 --> 01:35:00,402
感谢弗吉尼亚大学喧嚣合唱团的表演 女士们先生们
The University of Virginia Hullabahoos, Iadies and gentlemen.

1320
01:35:01,404 --> 01:35:02,404
终于到了
There they are.

1321
01:35:02,489 --> 01:35:04,281
一 二 三 加油!
One, two, three, swag!

1322
01:35:04,366 --> 01:35:08,786
欢迎回到大学生无伴奏合唱国际锦标赛
Welcome back to the International Championship of Collegiate A Cappella.

1323
01:35:09,412 --> 01:35:14,124
下一支队伍 不介绍相信各位也了解了 不过我还是要介绍一下!
This next group, they need no introduction, but I'll do it anyway!

1324
01:35:14,209 --> 01:35:17,878
嘿
Hey.

1325
01:35:17,962 --> 01:35:19,004
祝你们好运
Good luck.

1326
01:35:19,756 --> 01:35:21,882
谢了 你们也是
Thanks. You, too.

1327
01:35:21,966 --> 01:35:24,718
巴顿大学的刺儿头小子合唱团!
The Barden University Treblemakers!

1328
01:38:08,132 --> 01:38:11,051
噢 刺儿头小子的结尾一如既往的精彩
Oh, the Trebles closing it strong like always.

1329
01:38:11,135 --> 01:38:14,930
非常棒 今晚很难有其他队伍超越他们了
Absolutely tight. It's gonna be very hard to beat that tonight.

1330
01:38:15,014 --> 01:38:17,891
其他队伍也有他们精心准备的作品 约翰
Every other group has their work cut out for them, John.

1331
01:38:17,976 --> 01:38:22,062
盖尔 很高兴我们不用去竞争了 谢天谢地 那种日子结束啦
I'm glad it's not us anymore, Gail. Those days are over, thank goodness.

1332
01:38:22,146 --> 01:38:25,232
特别是他们不要我们回去后
Especially since they wouldn't have us back.

1333
01:38:25,316 --> 01:38:28,735
好了 表演如何?
All right. How about that?

1334
01:38:28,820 --> 01:38:29,945
巴顿大学的刺儿头小子合唱团
The Barden University Treblemakers.

1335
01:38:30,029 --> 01:38:31,113
我爱你们 三八们
I love you, awesome nerds.

1336
01:38:31,573 --> 01:38:33,657
你们是最棒的
Yeah, you guys are the best.

1337
01:38:34,909 --> 01:38:38,996
虽然你们有些人特别瘦 不过我相信 你们都有一颗胖胖的心
Even though some of you are pretty thin, I think that you all have fat hearts,

1338
01:38:39,998 --> 01:38:42,124
那就足够了
and that's what matters.

1339
01:38:42,208 --> 01:38:44,501
我们加油吧 好吗?
Okay, let's just smash this. Okay?

1340
01:38:44,836 --> 01:38:49,506
女士们先生们 有请巴顿贝拉合唱团!
Ladies and gentlemen, the Barden Bellas!

1341
01:38:51,509 --> 01:38:54,511
噢 天啊 看到了吗?
Oh, my goodness gracious. Will you look at this?

1342
01:38:54,762 --> 01:38:58,557
贝拉的制服竟然不见了 她们有了新的面貌
Gone are those Bella uniforms and this is a whole new look for them,

1343
01:38:58,641 --> 01:39:00,309
真是正点 正点 正点
and it is hot, hot, hot.

1344
01:39:00,393 --> 01:39:02,894
约翰 她们让我都想变男人了
John, these girls could turn me.

1345
01:39:07,692 --> 01:39:10,027
我们爱你 贝拉!
We love you, Bellas!

1346
01:39:17,910 --> 01:39:20,704
一 二 三 四
One, two, three, four.

1347
01:43:03,010 --> 01:43:04,511
干得好 贝卡!
Way to go, Beca!

1348
01:43:22,113 --> 01:43:23,363
这场演出太精彩了!
What a show!

1349
01:43:23,447 --> 01:43:27,576
约翰 我想我们刚刚见证了一段无伴奏合唱的历史
I think we have just seen some a cappella history being made, John.

1350
01:43:27,660 --> 01:43:31,538
而且是来自一个全女生的团体啊 盖尔 我从未预见到这种情况
And from an all-female group, Gail. I could never have called this one.

1351
01:43:31,622 --> 01:43:34,249
当然了 你内心一直厌恶女生
Never. Well, you are a misogynist at heart,

1352
01:43:34,333 --> 01:43:36,376
你也自然不可能料想到这群女孩会赢
so there's no way you would have bet on these girls to win.

1353
01:43:36,460 --> 01:43:37,460
确实啊
Absolutely.

1354
01:43:41,132 --> 01:43:43,133
是不是很不可思议? 哇!
Weren't they incredible? Wow!

1355
01:43:45,887 --> 01:43:50,140
女士们先生们 让我们再次为巴顿贝拉鼓掌!
Ladies and gentlemen, let's give it up again for the Barden Bellas!

1356
01:43:52,435 --> 01:43:54,895
早告诉过你 结尾才是最精彩的
Told you. Endings are the best part.

1357
01:43:54,979 --> 01:43:56,146
你真是个怪胎
You're such a weirdo.

1358
